                <zone forceUpdate='true' h='18611' id='48' type-v2='text' w='12845' x='24113' y='81111'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run fontcolor='#0461ba'>Jade customers have the highest average customer value (~$2.97M), outperforming Gold, Silver, and Platinum segments.</run>
